== Births == * {{ill|Bunei|ja|文永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5 ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1268|ja|1268th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Keizan Jōkin|ja|瑩山紹瑾|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the fourth patriarch of Japanese {{ill|Sōtō Zen|ja|Sōtō Zen|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (+ {{ill|1325|ja|1325th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) (Some sources suggest {{ill|Bunei|ja|文永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1 instead).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Meiwa (era)|ja|Meiwa|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1764|ja|1764th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Munekatsu|ja|徳川宗春|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} <ref>『御系譜』『系譜』（both included in 名古屋叢書三編 第一巻）</ref>, 7th {{ill|Owari Domain|ja|尾張藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} lord (* {{ill|1696|ja|1696th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871st year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 20|ja|11月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Andō Nobumasa|ja|安藤信正|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Rōjū|ja|老中|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 5th lord of {{ill|Iwakitaira Domain|ja|磐城平藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|1819|ja|1819th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
