'''October 8''' is the 8th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} . 

== Events ==
* {{ill|Meireki|ja|明暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  1 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1655|ja|1655th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 5|ja|11月5日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Joseon Tongsinsa|ja|朝鮮通信使|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  audience with {{ill|Tokugawa Ietsuna|ja|徳川家綱|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} .

== Births ==
* {{ill|Bunei|ja|文永|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  5 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1268|ja|1268th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Keizan Jōkin|ja|瑩山紹瑾|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , the fourth patriarch of Japanese {{ill|Sōtō Zen|ja|Sōtō Zen|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  (+ {{ill|1325|ja|1325th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) (Some sources suggest {{ill|Bunei|ja|文永|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  1 instead).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Meiwa (era)|ja|Meiwa|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  1 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1764|ja|1764th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Munekatsu|ja|徳川宗春|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} <ref>『御系譜』『系譜』（both included in 名古屋叢書三編 第一巻）</ref>, 7th {{ill|Owari Domain|ja|尾張藩|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  lord (* {{ill|1696|ja|1696th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  4 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1871|ja|1871st year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 20|ja|11月20日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Andō Nobumasa|ja|安藤信正|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Rōjū|ja|老中|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , 5th lord of {{ill|Iwakitaira Domain|ja|磐城平藩|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  (* {{ill|1819|ja|1819th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

