== Events == * {{ill|Meireki|ja|明暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1655|ja|1655th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 5|ja|11月5日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Joseon Tongsinsa|ja|朝鮮通信使|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} audience with {{ill|Tokugawa Ietsuna|ja|徳川家綱|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .
== Births == * {{ill|Bunei|ja|文永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1268|ja|1268th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Keizan Jōkin|ja|瑩山紹瑾|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , the fourth patriarch of Japanese {{ill|Sōtō Zen|ja|Sōtō Zen|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (+ {{ill|1325|ja|1325th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) (Some sources suggest {{ill|Bunei|ja|文永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1 instead).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Meiwa (era)|ja|Meiwa|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1764|ja|1764th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Munekatsu|ja|徳川宗春|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} <ref>『御系譜』『系譜』（both included in 名古屋叢書三編 第一巻）</ref>, 7th {{ill|Owari Domain|ja|尾張藩|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} lord (* {{ill|1696|ja|1696th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 4 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871st year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 20|ja|11月20日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Andō Nobumasa|ja|安藤信正|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Rōjū|ja|老中|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , 5th lord of {{ill|Iwakitaira Domain|ja|磐城平藩|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (* {{ill|1819|ja|1819th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
